<p>Tax havens should not be a problem. After all, crypto-currencies are effectively a sort of a tax haven, accessible to all, and the whole point of this article is to find out how to deal with that. The whole assumtion is apparently that, while (monetary) property tax can be avoided by using tax havens, VAT can not.</p>
