<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2011/05/19/the-information-policy-case-for-flat-tax-and-basic-income/?replytocom=83961#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-83961", "83961", "respond", "7361")'>RESPOND TO THIS</a> </div>
