<li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-83997">
<div id="comment-83997">
<div class="commentnumber">32</div>
<div class="comment-author vcard">
<div class="avatar-commentnumber"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/ee39f3e1215721b53249c4bbcc75009e?s=60&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D60&amp;r=R' class='avatar avatar-60 photo' height='60' width='60'/></div> <cite class="fn"><a href='http://robertwensman.wordpress.com/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Robert Wensman</a></cite> </div>
