<p>You can&#8217;t have VAT. What&#8217;s makes you think that if people will be evading income tax, then companies will not evade VAT?</p>
<p>VAT is a stupid tax because it taxes not only consumption, but services. Services help use time and resources better. You want to tax pure consumption, tax the resources: trees, oil, water, coal, chemicals, etc. and do tax them HIGH because that will make people use them in smarter way, limiting our ecologic footprint. Stop taxing the fact that one person is doing something better and using less resources than other!</p>
