<div class="comment-author vcard">
<div class="avatar-commentnumber"><img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/35a487601bc6d5811a215cbdb3394c32?s=60&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F1.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D60&amp;r=R' class='avatar avatar-60 photo' height='60' width='60'/></div> <cite class="fn">Carl</cite> </div>
