<div class="commentnumber">79</div>
<div class="comment-author vcard">
<div class="avatar-commentnumber"><img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/5c3f613da03ed3a932c78451c3b35a08?s=60&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F1.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D60&amp;r=R' class='avatar avatar-60 photo' height='60' width='60'/></div> <cite class="fn"><a href='http://themonetaryfuture.blogspot.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Jon Matonis</a></cite> </div>
