<p>Rick, I am thrilled that you get the macro-economic impact that is forthcoming due to the bitcoin ecosystem. However, it is a shame that you intertwine that with support for a welfare nanny State. Welfare is just as immoral as taxation and fortunately free individuals that only spend within the bitcoin ecosystem will be immune from proposed consumption taxes as well.</p>
