<p>I don&#8217;t know if you&#8217;ve already covered the issue in the comments but the problem I see with a basic income is it&#8217;s flat payment nature when life aint like that. The pensioner with dementia and no relatives/support network might require care costing $50,000pa, whilst someone who&#8217;s unemployed might require $20,000pa.</p>
